choices.text:
### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for 7 days.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews
### Assistant:

Day 1:
- Breakfast: Oatmeal with fruit and nuts (excluding almonds, pistachios, and cashews)
- Lunch: Grilled chicken salad with avocado and vegetables
- Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables

Day 2:
- Breakfast: Smoothie bowl with fruit and nut butter (excluding almonds, pistachios, and cashews)
- Lunch: Turkey lettuce wraps with avocado and tomato
- Dinner: Grilled tofu with roasted vegetables

Day 3:
- Breakfast: Greek yogurt with fruit and granola (excluding honey)
- Lunch: Quinoa salad with grilled chicken and vegetables
- Dinner: Baked cod with roasted vegetables

Day 4:
- Breakfast: Omelette with vegetables and whole wheat toast
- Lunch: Grilled shrimp skewers with vegetables
- Dinner: Baked salmon with roasted vegetables
